9dbda09b4660c69db629f/62844944d5a974bc56434b63_cta-arrow.svg" loading="lazy" width="50" height="30" alt="Arrow" class="arrow"/></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class="testimonial24_arrow left w-slider-arrow-left"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4660c69db629f/6259dbda09b46677d6db62d9_icon_slider-arrow-left.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Arrow" class="image-22"/></div><div class="testimonial24_arrow w-slider-arrow-right"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4660c69db629f/6259dbda09b466b892db62df_icon_slider-arrow-right.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Arrow" class="image-21"/></div><div class="testimonial24_slide-nav w-slider-nav w-slider-nav-invert"></div></div></div></div></section><div class="section small"><div data-w-id="6da9a9ea-46d7-b655-e16d-b2f6ba728f22" style="opacity:0" class="container-large w-container"><div class="max-width-large-2"><div class="padding-right"><h2 class="heading-24">Have a Specific Design Project in Mind?</h2></div><div class="home-services"><p class="center">My expertise extends beyond Amazon listing graphics, A+ content, and email marketing design. I can also assist with other graphic design needs, including brochures, websites, landing pages, popups, social media, display ads, sell sheets, and sales decks. I do it all! Well, almost.</p></div></div><div class="button-wrrapper"><a href="/contact" class="button-main w-button">let&#x27;s get started</a></div></div></div><div class="section padding-vertical"><div class="container-featured w-container"><div data-w-id="107e7f76-2daf-45b7-c821-8d659736cf88" style="opacity:0" class="feature-heading"><div class="heading-large stylized"><span class="standout">Featured </span><br/>Works</div></div><div class="w-layout-grid feature-grid"><div id="w-node-aa721fde-18b1-9c92-d3f2-194925ec8f19-033e65ba" data-w-id="aa721fde-18b1-9c92-d3f2-194925ec8f19" style="opacity:0" class="feature-1-container"><div class="feature-1"><div class="acccessibility-featured-text">Female floating on water with a Better Booch can</div><a href="https://www.marissaputtagio.com/work/better-booch" class="feature-image-link">Female floating in water with a can of Better Booch</a></div><a href="https://www.marissaputtagio.com/work/better-booch" class="feature-text-link w-inline-block"><div class="feature-text-container"><div class="featured-wrapper"><div class="feature-work-title">Better Booch</div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4660c69db629f/62844944d5a974bc56434b63_cta-arrow.svg" loading="lazy" width="50" height="35" alt="Arrow" class="feature-work-arrow"/></div></div></a></div><div id="w-node-_44e3321a-a40f-272a-72ca-5d00e00213bf-033e65ba" data-w-id="44e3321a-a40f-272a-72ca-5d00e00213bf" style="opacity:0" class="feature-2-container"><div class="feature-2"><div class="acccessibility-featured-text">Blurred female with a Mojo gummy bag</div></div><a href="https://www.marissaputtagio.com/work/stacked-skincare" class="feature-image-link">Female holding a bag of Mojo on a gradient background</a><a href="https://www.marissaputtagio.com/work/stacked-skincare" target="_blank" class="feature-text-link w-inline-block"><div class="feature-text-container"><div class="featured-wrapper"><div class="feature-work-title">StackedSkincare</div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4660c69db629f/62844944d5a974bc56434b63_cta-arrow.svg" loading="lazy" width="50" height="35" alt="Arrow" class="feature-work-arrow"/></div></div></a></div><div id="w-node-_74b95606-da1e-96f7-7b7c-cd95fa95e12a-033e65ba" data-w-id="74b95606-da1e-96f7-7b7c-cd95fa95e12a" style="opacity:0" class="feature-3-container"><div class="feature-3"><div class="acccessibility-featured-text">Female hugging a cheeseburger pillow</div><a href="https://www.marissaputtagio.com/work/little-hunter" class="feature-image-link">Female using Stacked Skincare dermaplaning tool</a></div><a href="https://www.marissaputtagio.com/work/little-hunter" class="feature-text-link w-inline-bl