</style></div><div class="container-large w-container"><p class="text-size-medium text-align-right">the crowd has spoken</p><div data-delay="4000" data-animation="slide" class="testimonial-component w-slider" data-autoplay="true" data-easing="ease" data-hide-arrows="false" data-disable-swipe="false" data-autoplay-limit="0" data-nav-spacing="15" data-duration="500" data-infinite="false"><div class="testimonial-mask w-slider-mask"><div class="testimonial w-slide"><div class="testimonial-content"><div class="margin-vertical margin-medium"><div class="testimonial-text">&quot;Just love Marissa&#x27;s work! So thrilled with the results. Working with her was no-nonsense, and I felt confident and at ease that she would deliver. It&#x27;s clear that she understands what needs to be done and offers helpful feedback to allow me to be able to edit the templates she provided. I appreciate every aspect of my experience working with her!&quot;</div></div><p class="testimonial-name">Leyda, Thalian Apparel</p></div></div><div class="testimonial w-slide"><div class="testimonial-content"><div class="margin-vertical margin-medium"><div class="testimonial-text">&quot;Working with Marissa was the best experience. She will meet your deadlines, always be in constant communication with you, and even guide you to make more efficient decisions with your email marketing strategy.&quot;</div></div><p class="testimonial-name">Andrew, Huevies</p></div></div><div class="testimonial w-slide"><div class="testimonial-content"><div class="margin-vertical margin-medium"><div class="testimonial-text">&quot;She is reliable, detailed, talented, and extremely easy to work with. She is not only exceptional at her work; she truly cares about her clients. She is a pleasure to work with, and I can&#x27;t recommend her enough.&quot;</div></div><p class="testimonial-name">Josy, PBH Foods</p></div></div><div class="testimonial w-slide"><div class="testimonial-content"><div class="margin-vertical margin-medium"><div class="testimonial-text">&quot;Marissa was absolutely amazing to work with. I gave her very little in the way of guidance and she knocked it out of the park. I would recommend her to anyone. Thank you Marissa, for taking one more thing off of my plate!&quot;</div></div><p class="testimonial-name">Allie, Charlie Swims</p></div></div><div class="testimonial w-slide"><div class="testimonial-content"><div class="margin-vertical margin-medium"><div class="testimonial-text">&quot;Marissa is a highly talented designer. Working with her was easy; her experience showed through the assets created and the initiative taken to include ideas that weren&#x27;t included in the brief.&quot;</div></div><p class="testimonial-name">Leo, Gwella</p></div></div><div class="testimonial w-slide"><div class="testimonial-content"><div class="margin-vertical margin-medium"><div class="testimonial-text">&quot;Marissa was a joy to work with! As a small business owner and someone who definitely does not have strength in email marketing, she delivered great quality work with good communication and made it easy for me! I am already lining up my next project for Marissa and can&#x27;t wait to get it going.&quot;</div></div><p class="testimonial-name">Jeremy, YES Bar</p></div></div><div class="testimonial w-slide"><div class="testimonial-content"><div class="margin-vertical margin-medium"><div class="testimonial-text">&quot;Marissa was exceptional in handling our email marketing through Klaviyo. Her graphic design skills are shown through the visually stunning email templates she created. She also executed technically sound campaigns, making the entire process seamless. Her communication was top-notch. Highly recommend for anyone in need of email marketing and design services.&quot;</div></div><p class="testimonial-name">Isaac, Astrokid</p></div></div></div><div class="testimonial11_arrow left w-slider-arrow-left"><img width="50" height="50" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4660c69db629f/62844944d5a974bc56434b63_cta-arrow.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Arrow" class="image-7"/></div><div class="testimonial11_arrow w-slider-arrow-right"><img width="50" height="50" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4660c69db629f/62844944d5a974bc56434b63_cta-arrow.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Arrow" class="image-51"/></div><div class="testimonial11_slide-nav w-slider-nav"></div></div></div></section><div class="section text-align-left background-color-purple"><div class="container-large centered w-container"><div class="padding-bottom"><h3 class="heading-large text-align-center">The More You Know</h3></div><div class="posts-collection-list w-dyn-list"><div role="list" class="collection-list w-dyn-items"><div role="listitem" class="mix w-dyn-item"><a href="/blog/boost-your-amazon-listings" class="blog-link-block w-inline-block"><div class="accessibility-blog-name">Boost Your Amazon Listings with A+ or Premium A+ Content</div></a><img height="400" loading="lazy" width="600" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4668cb5db62c2/64eb8aff16981179a843689c_Amazon-A%2B-Content.jpg" alt="Amazon A+ Examples" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4668cb5db62c2/64eb8aff16981179a843689c_Amazon-A%2B-Content-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4668cb5db62c2/64eb8aff16981179a843689c_Amazon-A%2B-Content-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4668cb5db62c2/64eb8aff16981179a843689c_Amazon-A%2B-Content-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4668cb5db62c2/64eb8aff16981179a843689c_Amazon-A%2B-Content.jpg 1500w" class="blog-thumbnail"/><div class="blog-item-content"><div class="blog-info"><div class="category-link">Amazon</div><div class="blog-time">🕒 8 Min Read</div></div><div class="blog-content"><div class="blog-title featured">Boost Your Amazon Listings with A+ or Premium A+ Content</div><p class="blog-summary">Compare the differences between Amazon A+ and Premium A+ Content and discover how to create beautiful graphics for your listings that can help you attract new customers and increase conversions.</p></div><div class="blog-cta"><div class="blog-cta-text">read more</div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4660c69db629f/62844944d5a974bc56434b63_cta-arrow.svg" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" alt="Arrow" class="blog-cta-arrow"/></div></div></div><div role="listitem" class="mix w-dyn-item"><a href="/blog/why-klaviyo" class="blog-link-block w-inline-block"><div class="accessibility-blog-name">7 Reasons Why I Recommend Klaviyo to all My Clients</div></a><img height="400" loading="lazy" width="600" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4668cb5db62c2/63deb61511b873c2a19d34da_Blog.jpg" alt="Klaviyo" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4668cb5db62c2/63deb61511b873c2a19d34da_Blog-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4668cb5db62c2/63deb61511b873c2a19d34da_Blog-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4668cb5db62c2/63deb61511b873c2a19d34da_Blog-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4668cb5db62c2/63deb61511b873c2a19d34da_Blog.jpg 1200w" class="blog-thumbnail"/><div class="blog-item-content"><div class="blog-info"><div class="category-link">Email</div><div class="blog-time">🕒 8 Min Read</div></div><div class="blog-content"><div class="blog-title featured">7 Reasons Why I Recommend Klaviyo to all My Clients</div><p class="blog-summary">Email marketing can be tricky. But it doesn&#x27;t have to be with the right platform. Here are 7 reasons why Klaviyo is the best platform for your email marketing efforts.</p></div><div class="blog-cta"><div class="blog-cta-text">read more</div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6259dbda09b4660c69db629f/62844944d5a974bc56434b63_cta-arrow.svg" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" alt="Arrow" class="